### Test 1 : Ajout d'un etudiant -> attendu 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/etudiants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matricule": "ET001",
  "prenom": "Moussa",
  "nom": "Diallo",
  "email": "moussa@universite.sn",
  "dateNaissance": "2003-04-15",
  "lieuNaissance": "Thies",
  "nationalite": "Senegalaise"
}

### Test 2 : Matricule deja existant -> attendu 409 Conflict
POST http://localhost:8080/etudiants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matricule": "ET001",
  "prenom": "Awa",
  "nom": "Ndiaye",
  "email": "awa@universite.sn",
  "dateNaissance": "2002-01-10",
  "lieuNaissance": "Dakar",
  "nationalite": "Senegalaise"
}

### Test 3 : Email deja existant -> attendu 409 Conflict
POST http://localhost:8080/etudiants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matricule": "ET002",
  "prenom": "Awa",
  "nom": "Ndiaye",
  "email": "moussa@universite.sn",
  "dateNaissance": "2002-01-10",
  "lieuNaissance": "Dakar",
  "nationalite": "Senegalaise"
}

### Test 4 : Champ obligatoire manquant (prenom vide) -> attendu 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/etudiants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matricule": "ET003",
  "prenom": "",
  "nom": "Fall",
  "email": "fall@universite.sn",
  "dateNaissance": "2001-05-20",
  "lieuNaissance": "Saint-Louis",
  "nationalite": "Senegalaise"
}

### Test 5 : Recherche d'un etudiant inexistant -> attendu 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/etudiants/100

### Test 6 : Suppression d'un etudiant existant -> attendu 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8080/etudiants/1

### Bonus : Liste triee par nom
GET http://localhost:8080/etudiants?tri=nom

### Bonus : Recherche par matricule
GET http://localhost:8080/etudiants/matricule/ET001

### Modification d'un etudiant existant -> attendu 200 OK
PUT http://localhost:8080/etudiants/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matricule": "ET001",
  "prenom": "Moussa",
  "nom": "Diallo",
  "email": "moussa.diallo@universite.sn",
  "dateNaissance": "2003-04-15",
  "lieuNaissance": "Thies",
  "nationalite": "Senegalaise"
}
